chart.name: Duration
chart.programText:
A = data('function.duration', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='average').mean().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Longest Average Durations
chart.programText:
A = data('function.duration', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('function.invocations', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).top(count=10).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Duration by Version
chart.programText:
A = data('function.duration', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum').sum(by=['gcp_function_version']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('function.invocations', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum').sum(by=['gcp_function_version']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Version Errors Heatmap
chart.programText:
A = data('function.invocations', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=2).sum(by=['gcp_function_version']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('function.errors', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=2).sum(by=['gcp_function_version']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/A).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Invocation Duration
chart.programText:
A = data('function.duration', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='average').mean(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: % of total errors by function
chart.programText:
A = data('function.errors', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('function.errors', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/A).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.description: The number of times a function is invoked in response to an event or invocation API call.
chart.name: Invocations
chart.programText:
A = data('function.invocations', rollup='sum').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('function.errors', rollup='sum').sum().publish(label='B')
C = data('function.cold_starts', rollup='sum').sum().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Duration 1d % change for slowest 5
chart.programText:
A = data('function.duration', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1d').sum(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('function.invocations', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gcf_wrapper'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1d').sum(by=['gcp_function_name']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).top(by=['gcp_function_name'], count=5).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).timeshift('1d').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C/D-1).scale(100).publish(label='E')
